## Tourism  

Val-de-Marne offers a surprising variety of cultural and leisure attractions:  

* [Château de Vincennes](/Ch%C3%A2teau_de_Vincennes) – a former royal residence with an expansive park and the famous keep.  
* [Roseraie de L'Haÿ](/Roseraie_de_L%27Ha%C3%AF) – a historic rose garden celebrated for its collection of heritage roses.  
* An oddity from the [Musée Fragonard d'Alfort](/Mus%C3%A9e_Fragonard_d%27Alfort) – a museum of anatomy and pathology that draws curiosity seekers.  
* [Vincennes Racecourse](/Vincennes_Racecourse) – a historic horse‑racing venue.  
* [Paris Zoological Park](/Paris_Zoological_Park) (formerly Vincennes Zoo) – a large zoo relocated to the Bois de Vincennes.  

